cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.DL

This paper deals with machine learning and natural language processing techniques to infer concept prerequisite relations from online educational resources. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, since the paper deals with online educational resources, it could also be categorized under cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.DL (Digital Libraries).
